00:04:24.020 --> 00:04:26.370
Halle Berry in Gothika

00:04:26.370 --> 00:04:30.660
Robert Downey Jr. has been known as a prolific
actor for a long time to fans and the film

00:04:30.660 --> 00:04:31.660
industry alike.

00:04:31.660 --> 00:04:36.220
His role as Chaplin garnered him a much deserved
Academy Award nomination and today he wows

00:04:36.220 --> 00:04:39.120
us with his performance as Iron Man in the
marvel films.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:43.190
He gets so into his roles that he sometimes
forgets himself and during a scene with Halle

00:04:43.190 --> 00:04:46.220
Berry in Gothika he accidentally hurt the
actress.

00:04:46.220 --> 00:04:50.620
The scene is when he had to restrain Berry
and hold her arms down, as he held her down

00:04:50.620 --> 00:04:51.800
he broke her arm.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:55.930
The moment RDJ heard the pop, he stopped and
she was treated, they are still friends today

00:04:55.930 --> 00:05:03.410
and she holds nothing against him.

00:05:03.410 --> 00:05:05.639
Channing Tatum in Foxcatcher

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:09.580
Channing Tatum wanted to show his acting chops
with 2014’s Foxcatcher.

00:05:09.580 --> 00:05:13.370
In the scene where his character has a breakdown
in a hotel room, he breaks a mirror with his

00:05:13.370 --> 00:05:16.139
head but despite precautions he still got
hurt.

00:05:16.139 --> 00:05:19.840
The mirror had a plastic sleeve attached to
it to protect Tatum but the actor went too

00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:22.800
far and bashed his head three times into the
mirror.

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:27.000
He broke the mirror, the frame and the wall
behind the mirror, not to mention he cut his

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:28.000
head too.

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:35.070
You can actually see his blood in the movie,
no makeup artist was needed.

00:05:35.070 --> 00:05:37.650
Vin Diesel in Fast and Furious 7

00:05:37.650 --> 00:05:41.410
Fist fights with Jason Stratham, beatings
with lead pipes, being slammed against cars

00:05:41.410 --> 00:05:46.289
and minor concussions sounds like a typical
day on set of the Fast and Furious franchise.

00:05:46.289 --> 00:05:50.400
Especially if you are the star and producer
of these films, Vin Diesel.

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:54.650
During production of Fast and Furious 7, Diesel
hurt himself and was rushed to the hospital

00:05:54.650 --> 00:05:55.960
because of a concussion.

00:05:55.960 --> 00:06:00.160
He doesn’t know how he got the concussion
because the day he did receive it he was performing

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:01.270
numerous stunts.

00:06:01.270 --> 00:06:05.259
We’re betting Michele Rodriguez got upset
with him and showed him why she’s one of

00:06:05.259 --> 00:06:07.630
the coolest female action stars around.

