The Rock in Central Intelligence

00:06:19.970 --> 00:06:24.330
Two guys that love social media as much as
social media loves them is Dwayne Johnson

00:06:24.330 --> 00:06:28.340
and Kevin Hart, so when they were making their
film Central Intelligence Johnson decided

00:06:28.340 --> 00:06:29.669
