00:06:29.669 --> 00:06:34.000
He showed how even a broken finger can’t
make him shed a tear with an Instagram video

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:37.460
but it’s easy not to shed a tear when you’re
using a prosthetic finger.

00:06:37.460 --> 00:06:41.919
The actor was fine but we bet he wished he
was using a prosthetic head when Hart slams

00:06:41.919 --> 00:06:44.320
