head.

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:48.470
He’s lucky the pointy side of the tile didn’t
get him and Hart is lucky The Rock has a sense

00:06:48.470 --> 00:06:51.520
of humor because he laughed at the body-builders
misfortune.

